<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. En un zuo vawnchawih henkawl ei sutpa,
 A min Kalvri tang achun;
 Thing hansie dawl chungah a khaikang ui,
 Kei di'n A thisan lul a luong ie,

[V2]
 Hukdampa nak thiengtho achun,
 Thisan leh tui ahung luong dawk;
 Ka suihlung in ngilhlo zen hen,
 Gilo thienna lui chu.

[V3]
 2. Ziechun hehpihna damtui thieng a luong.
 Hukdampa thihna mun achun;
 Sun leh zan in zie chun va leng inla,
 Ka thagau na Hukdampa kiengah.

[V4]
 3. Kuole zie thisan lui a kisil chu,
 A gitlouh vuk sanga vam ding;
 &quot;Aw na gitloh nin chu silthieng inla,
 Hung in aw,' tin Hukdampa'n ei sam.

[V5]
 4. Vakmang santa puong ka khawvel ahin,
 Ka hehpih ka Lal Hukdampa;
 Aw Na thagau thiengtho in ei pui in,
 Na mel deihum chu ei muhsak in.</lyrics>
<title>Gitloh Thienna Lui</title>
<author>Zasiama</author>
<hymn_number>41</hymn_number>
</song>